(2) Monitor for permitted processing at the external interfaces to the system and at key internal boundaries within the system; <br>[2: Implementation Statement]<br>
(3) Document each processing exception and require AO approval; and <br>[3: Implementation Statement]<br>
(4) Review and remove exceptions that are no longer supported. <br>[4: Implementation Statement]<br>

